Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.35,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要過度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  6  7  8  9…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝天椒要切成絲放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多炒會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了  速水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪你想繼續做料理到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人只要活著就少不了吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做料理之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是死亡之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是可以考慮偶爾用些其它方法來引春香注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方說  你看  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10  11  12  13
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14  15  16  17…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是16
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這個越來越冷的季節是必不可少的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始努力說不定能趕在聖誕節之前送出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提從今年的流行和我的喜好上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦這種感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  加油試試看吧  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒假到來之前完成它…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了南春香開始做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術上的確進步了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還沒有讓她笑過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前連話都沒有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不成熟的雙手不論做什麼都不成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來我令南春香展開笑容的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再開始織東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓她和女兒們得到溫暖的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香說過喜歡織的東西喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼從今天開始我也喜歡織東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31  誒？  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  繼續吧
