Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希穿了新大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為變冷了  不過今天更冷了一個級別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  特別冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子的圍巾毛絨絨的感覺很厚很暖和  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個很暖和所以很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希的大衣感覺也很暖和真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是新買的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希問問題的意圖很容易懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子能理解我問題的意圖真是幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有點煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  想問你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味的牛奶可可和加了過多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得哪個更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可？咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為選哪個而煩惱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在打比方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味牛奶可可和放了過多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道淡加點就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一邊只要再加些咖啡就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還要加熱水和糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把放多了的味道調回去會很難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可可更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嗎  淳子也這樣想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真希今天早上穿的大衣是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「淡味的牛奶可可」色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:06:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個都是不對的麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  你怎樣想？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個到底是重複了呢還是沒重複呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白意圖的二選一問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會不會選哪個都是不對的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個重複了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有重複嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能兩個都不是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得真希新大衣的顏色和南春香大衣的顏色重複了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本身並不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上說答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是少見的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複了也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拿鐵咖啡的顏色進入到視線的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會困惑也是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無處可去的心情該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無計可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問為什麼  無處可去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些問題似乎多想無用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時裏說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的價值是由被男生告白的次數決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那句話的是競爭對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那之後被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管這樣我覺得還是有一番道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何內田  最近很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:43.02,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也無濟於事的話還是不要去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我怎樣才能受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  淳子  老實說你很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？果然很受歡迎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有受歡迎秘訣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣才能受歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣才能受歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我什麼都沒有想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂內田  什麼都不想就會受歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？夏奈那種事情可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你們在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來淳子是被稱為魔女的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定擁有魔法之類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的魔法使？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一個說害羞的話也不臉紅的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種事情  淳子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我受歡迎的秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我戀愛的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上皇家奶茶色的大衣之類的會好一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  有皇家奶茶色的大衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  借我皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.87,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我什麼腦筋都沒動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.55,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好嘛拜託了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給你用的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼啊千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上了春香的皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就受歡迎了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把別人認成了南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空也在嘲笑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到下的這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂純白就是那樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  掀開窗簾就是滿面的銀色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來的時候窗簾已經被妹妹拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經相當的興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跳出窗外被雪埋上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹已經這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也像她那麼年輕也會跳出去被雪埋上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話真想雪再積得深一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就可以堆雪屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫馨的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會下雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.8度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  哪裏不舒服麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力  量了體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是低燒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐也來量體溫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變冷了  很怕感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的雪也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我先離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…還是扣上比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才量體溫之後忘記扣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用這種堅定又純真的少年的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  簡直就是滿面的純白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別特地把顏色說出來啊  純白什麼的別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為打開著一下子就充滿了視野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是故意的…什麼  興…興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來軟綿綿地非常柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛撲上去一定很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛…飛撲什麼的  就在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再年輕一些就會撲上去深埋進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有多大啊  不是跟我同歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來還真可惜  能再大一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你也看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.5也算正常體溫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還是有些乏力  不過加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我說  夏樹看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…還是說快要看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是白茫茫的一片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的純白色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也沒在看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明積了這麼多雪  是沒在看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  在生什麼氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為別的  都是因為夏樹那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個差勁的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不揍他一頓就嚥不下這口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口被那傢伙看了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是目不轉睛的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…剛才…夏樹他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還用少年純真的眼神說什麼純白很漂亮什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純白？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說他很興奮什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說看起來軟綿綿很柔軟的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飛撲上去什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飛撲上去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還說要是再年輕一些就危險了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說我已經老了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還說要是再大一點就好了  太差勁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
