Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:09.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萌發出無限的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:16.16,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Merry Christmas&Happy Christmas
