Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  一年之計好像在於元旦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是電子詞典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是圭子！
